OL,3,CTwo Leicestershire councils to receive
OL,4,Cemergency homelessness funding
OL,6,FTwo Leicestershire councils are to
OL,7,Freceive emergency homelessness funding.
OL,9,FThe #10 million pot of Government cash
OL,10,Fis being shared among local
OL,11,Fauthorities with the "highest need".
OL,13,FBoth Leicester City Council and
OL,14,FCharnwood Borough Council have been
OL,15,Foffered part of the funding.
OL,17,FSome #143,000 will go to the city,
OL,18,Fwhich is expecting to spend #16
OL,19,Fmillion on homelessness services this
OL,20,Ffinancial year. A further #42,000 is
OL,21,Fto be given to the borough authority.
