OL,3,CTwo Leicestershire councils to receive
OL,4,Cemergency homelessness funding
OL,6,FThe money is intended to "fund
OL,7,Fcritical services to prevent
OL,8,Fhomelessness and support people into
OL,9,Fsecure, stable housing".
OL,11,FAssistant mayor for housing Elly
OL,12,FCutkelvin welcomed the additional
OL,13,Ffunding.
OL,15,FShe said: "It will help us to provide
OL,16,Fadditional temporary accommodation
OL,17,Fover the winter months, and more
OL,18,Fsupport for entrenched rough sleepers
OL,19,Fto prevent them from going back onto
OL,20,Fthe streets.
