OL,6,F"We are still working on the details
OL,7,Fas to exactly how the money will be
OL,8,Fallocated, but are already working
OL,9,Fwith local charities One Roof, Help
OL,10,Fthe Homeless and Action Homeless to
OL,11,Fprovide extra services.
OL,13,F"This new funding will be on top of
OL,14,Fthe #16 million the city council
OL,15,Falready spends on preventing
OL,16,Fhomelessness, providing temporary
OL,17,Faccommodation and supporting rough
OL,18,Fsleepers each year."
