OL,6,FA Charnwood Borough Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We welcome any
OL,8,Fadditional funding from the Government
OL,9,Fin relation to homelessness.
OL,11,F"The council delivers a range of
OL,12,Fservices and initiatives to prevent
OL,13,Fand relieve homelessness and will use
OL,14,Fthe funds to support delivery of our
OL,15,Frecently updated Homelessness and
OL,16,FRough Sleeping Strategy 2024-29 which
OL,17,Fcan be found on our website."
OL,19,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,20,Fannounced the funding.
