OL,3,CTwo Leicestershire councils to receive
OL,4,Cemergency homelessness funding
OL,6,FShe said: "Anyone forced to sleep
OL,7,Frough on our streets represents a
OL,8,Fcomplete failure of the broken system
OL,9,Fwe've inherited. It's a national
OL,10,Fdisgrace, and we can't keep sticking
OL,11,Fplasters on it.
OL,13,F"We are approaching the harshest
OL,14,Fmonths of the year which is why we are
OL,15,Ftaking immediate action to reach
OL,16,Fanyone sleeping rough and help them
OL,17,Foff the streets this winter.
